text: José Felipe Rocha Costa (born 21 April, 1998) better known by the stage name of Zé Felipe also known by the acronym ZF, is a Brazilian singer-songwriter. His career began in 2013. Felipe was born in Goiânia, Brazil. He is married to the digital influencer Virginia Fonseca.
